Trackbacks only work if the full URL is included in a page's source, bit if the URL is created by a macro. So, for example, If I have a page with a link such as:

    http://jira:8080/browse/BLA-49

then trackbacks work fine, but if I have a link inside a macro, such as:

    {issue:BLA-50}

where the issue macro is defined as:

     <a href="http://jira:8080/browse/$param1">$param1</a>

then a trackback is not created.

